name: Out of the Red
description: Sad to see the end of the original HEN. They were my philosophy....$100 digital crap camera. But you had to be there...Here and Now...No photoshop, ever. This is where I was standing when I took it.  Black Mountain, NC. Oct 25, 2012. SHJw2OeHkbw is how you find us. How do you like them apples? In Honor of HEN. I will leave all images for free and up until I find out where I want to go next, if not here. Then I burn it all again.
